posts.post_content:
This one has a lot going on, decent back miscut, front ink shift from adjacent card (Campbell) and by far the sharpest corners I've seen for the grade.  Slab in the scan has been darkened/cleaned but it has no scratches or issues.

SOLD paypal delivered.
